In case you missed it, the writing rocket scientists at Payload Space dropp=
ed a 12k word deep, deep dive into everything happening in the Space Econom=
y on Monday. Payload covers the goings-on in space every day, so it can see=
m like any other business, but take a second to think about how crazy it is=
 that there=E2=80=99s a thriving and growing economy in space. And it=E2=80=
=99s only going to get crazier in the coming years=E2=80=A6=20
